overview: On February 24th Terminus 2 was live straight from the Kroc Center of Atlanta! This celebratory event was presented by Luxe Jewelers & features ROH World Champ Jon Gresham, Santana, Serena Deeb, Lio Rush, Sw3rve "The Realest" Strickland, Baron Black, Leon Ruff and many more!
title: Terminus 2
